subsection.def:
Chairperson (主席)
                means the Chairperson of the Authority referred to in section 1(1)(a) of
                    Schedule 9;

committee (委員會),
                in relation to the Authority, means a committee established under section 27(1)
                    of Schedule 9;

director (董事)
                includes any person occupying the position of director (by whatever name
                called);

officer (高級人員), in
                relation to a company, includes a director, manager and company secretary of the
                company;

trade member (業界成員) means—(a)an individual who is engaged in the business of a licensed travel
